Birks Group Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















birks group inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Retail - Discretionary
Sub-Industry: Jewelry & Watch Stores
Birks Group Inc. is a North American luxury retailer, designer, manufacturer, and wholesaler of fine jewelry, timepieces, sterling silverware, and gifts.  The Company has stores operating across Canada, and in Florida and Georgia, both located in the United States.




